Commentary Text: Riyan Parag to Pant, out Pant Run Out!! Direct hit and Pant is gone, I reckon! He's walking. Brilliant work from Parag. Pant nudged this full ball into the leg-side and set off for a non-existent single. Parag got to the ball quickly, picked it, turned and hit the bulls-eye at the bowler's end. The TV umpire was called, but Pant knew that he was a goner! Brilliant work from Parag and he's broken the fifty partnership! Big blow for Delhi.. Pant run out (Riyan Parag) 51(32) [4s-9]
